{"tid":505642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平被捕：詳列8控罪刑罰　最高可囚85年","createTime":"2017-12-21T10:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T13:58:09.000Z","uid":30169,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"97900ace2e275a40ca282ddf9cd39abfa4e77949","tid":505642,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171221/bknint-20171221110029027-1221_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171221%2Fbknint-20171221110029027-1221_17011_001.html&d=htCG9v2Oi4CqOgqrZktGLI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=cad0ce7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171221/bknint-20171221110029027-1221_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/184458_5942a958ab6390077de08059f802f4df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F184458_5942a958ab6390077de08059f802f4df.jpg&h=66dcf84c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何志平涉賄案，根據最新公開的美國法庭文件，其中一份是起訴表格，詳細列出何志平8項控罪的最高刑罰。若果所有控罪成立及刑期分期執行的話，何志平面臨最高監禁85年。<br />\n<br />\n起訴表格先列出被告資料，包括何志平的姓名、出生年份、囚禁地點、代表律師。表格之後詳細列出何志平被控的罪名，分別是1項串謀違反《海外反腐敗法》、4項違反《海外反腐敗法》、1項串謀洗錢、2項洗錢的罪名。<br />\n<br />\n其中，5項涉及《海外反腐敗法》的罪名，每項的最高刑罰為5年監禁及3年監外看管（Supervised Release）。串謀違反《海外反腐敗法》的最高罰款為25萬美元，違反《海外反腐敗法》則罰款10萬美元。至於3項涉及洗錢的罪名，每項的最高刑罰為20年監禁及3年監外看管，以及罰款50萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n表格同時寫明上述所有控罪均設有替代罰款，涉及《海外反腐敗法》的罪名列明有關金額是「犯案金錢上所得或所失的兩倍」，而涉及洗錢的罪名是「所涉及金額的兩倍」。根據案情，何志平涉提供290萬美元賄款，若以此金額計算，替代罰款金額可達580萬美元（約4524萬港元）<br />\n<br />\n駐紐約記者郭少華報道"},{"pid":"d25826c8bc22c2c77944e45f2843caea6ae02dc7","tid":505642,"uid":148438,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b053a8ea9fa5ce78b281817415914d285c353d91","tid":505642,"uid":48157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a9ec5bb8279c5d33fa0a6438c13cdd29d93b165","tid":505642,"uid":26752,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.breitbart.com/media/2017/02/used-condom-Joshua-Ganderson-Flickr-640x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.breitbart.com%2Fmedia%2F2017%2F02%2Fused-condom-Joshua-Ganderson-Flickr-640x480.jpg&h=9a2b2948&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8e1155c7cbf6d7dde8593eea534944fa54e6b84","tid":505642,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"85年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9782243da116214832da62fd4b2a0a82c44cdd5f","tid":505642,"uid":48157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ca4eecb0ee265caf33e19238eff2aff937ef494","tid":505642,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘過死刑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e18a1ca98465015270a14aca604747f7f6933d","tid":505642,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84ece83c0ceab9ef800befd8bdfad086f74eb32","tid":505642,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘過死刑</blockquote><br />\n放佢出黎仲慘過死刑"},{"pid":"1632c3e09e64cd541d5916d757d086dfeee04536","tid":505642,"uid":10504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:32:20.000Z"